ComicInfo.Summary:
Psychoanalyst Dr. Kropotkin psychoanalyzes various comic characters to diagnose their issues.
Significant moments in the lives of Lucky Luciano, the Addams Family and Jack Benny.
The Russian hero Popoff brutalizes peasants.
A tiny tot named Billy terrorizes a town.
Endings for the television programs The Millionaire, Lassie, The Lineup, Have Gun Will Travel, The Phil Silvers Show, Foreign Legionnaire, Highway Patrol, Medic, Racket Squad and The Dinah Shore Show.
